---
title: Plant-Based Protein & Cheese Tostadas with Long Green Pepper, Tomato Salsa & Hot Sauce Crema
description: We love a good taco, but you don’t need us to tell you how to make one—there are kits for that. Instead, we’re here to show you how to take Tex-Mex night to the next level. So enter the tostada, featuring a flat tortilla baked until crisp, with lots of surface area for piling it on. Thankfully, there are plenty of toppings in this recipe, and not just warmly-spiced ground plant-based protein and melty cheese—there’s also green pepper, tomato salsa, and a spicy sour cream.
